  "texts": [
    "Robotic systems present unique challenges due to their complex interactions with dynamic operating environments.",
    "These challenges include varying task loads, unpredictable external factors, and the necessity for precise timing and coordination.• Black-Box WCET Analysis: This study uses a black-box method to WCET analysis.",
    "Traditional WCET methods often require detailed knowledge of the system's hardware and software configurations, which can be restrictive and difficult to obtain.",
    "Our black-box method; however, only necessitates understanding the format of the software's inputs.",
    "This simplification broadens the applicability of our method, making it easier to adapt to different systems without requiring extensive, system-specific modifications.• Usage of RL: To the best of our knowledge, this work is the first to apply RL for WCET estimation."
  ],
